I was once playing mid and at some point in the 7th minute of the game the unthinkable happened: Nasus was walking down from top to gank my lane.

It turns out his slow is super fucking powerful and we got the kill. Once we got the kill he just... Started very slowly farming my lane. It turns out the Darius up top was freezing the lane too hard.
